<section class="pg-section" data-section="Transform Your Skin with Every Session">
  <h2 class="pg-h">Transform Your Skin with Every Session</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Discover why our dermaplaning facial is the perfect solution for achieving smooth, radiant skin that looks and feels amazing.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Instant Smoothness &amp; Glow</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Remove weeks of dead skin buildup and fine facial hair in one treatment. Walk out with visibly smoother, brighter skin that feels like silk and has a natural, healthy glow.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Enhanced Product Absorption</p>
  <p class="pg-text">After dermaplaning, your skincare products penetrate up to 5x deeper. Maximize the effectiveness of your serums, moisturizers, and treatments for better long-term results.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Flawless Makeup Application</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Say goodbye to patchy foundation and cakey concealer. Your makeup will glide on effortlessly and look airbrushed, lasting longer throughout the day.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Safe &amp; Gentle Process</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Unlike harsh chemical peels or abrasive scrubs, our dermaplaning facial is suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin. No irritation, no downtime - just beautiful results.</p>
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/dermaplaning-facial">Schedule Now</a>
