<section class="pg-section" data-section="What To Expect During Your 60-Minute Dermaplane Facial Experience">
  <h2 class="pg-h">What To Expect During Your 60-Minute Dermaplane Facial Experience</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Every step is designed for your comfort and results. Here's exactly what happens during your 60-minute treatment at our Millburn spa.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Consultation &amp; Skin Analysis (5-10 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Your esthetician starts with a one-on-one consultation to evaluate your skin's texture, tone, and sensitivity. Together, you'll discuss your goals so your treatment is customized to deliver the best possible results.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Deep Cleansing &amp; Preparation (10-15 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Your skin is gently cleansed using the Corthe Dermo Cleansing Foam to remove makeup, oils, and impurities. This prepares your pores for deep treatment and ensures maximum product absorption.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Professional Dermaplaning (15-20 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Using a sterile surgical blade, we gently exfoliate your skin at a 45-degree angle. This painless process removes dead skin cells and fine facial hair, revealing smooth, glowing skin underneath.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Serum &amp; Moisturizer Application (10-15 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">We finish with premium serums and moisturizer that penetrate deeply into your freshly exfoliated skin. SPF is applied to protect your glowing complexion. Additional treatments like hydrating masks are available as add-ons.</p>
  <a class="pg-btn" href="/dermaplaning-facial">Schedule Now</a>
</section>

